{"tid":93991,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"報章引消息：陳永棋稱　選委不支林鄭等於反中央","createTime":"2017-01-25T00:37:53.000Z","updateTime":"2017-01-25T01:38:52.000Z","uid":6604,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"ee3d626bff3d4bdb95e2d7a329e73f074e203d04","tid":93991,"uid":6604,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-25T00:37:53.000Z","msg":"《信報》及《明報》今天都引述不具名的消息指，據了解，身兼政協常委的工業界（第二）選委陳永棋，昨在廠商會與特首參選人林鄭月娥的會面上，表明林鄭是最適當及最有能力的特首人選，又稱誰人不支持林鄭，就等於不支持中央。<br />\n<br />\n《明報》政情專欄作者「李先知」又稱，據了解，陳永棋上午與曾俊華會面時，稱與對方相識多時，過往有很多合作接觸等；到下午與林鄭的會面中，已表明自己「一定會提名」林鄭，<span style=\"color: red;\">更當面明言誰人不支持林鄭，是等於反對中央</span>。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.thestandnews.com/media/photos/cache/chan_IMJp3_1200x0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thestandnews.com%2Fmedia%2Fphotos%2Fcache%2Fchan_IMJp3_1200x0.png&h=63f57ea9&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"e8f7d8db60af2e92518fc8585be7a91852bd0f45","tid":93991,"uid":22609,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-25T01:10:10.000Z","msg":"Lm薯片叔叔入唔到閳"},{"pid":"981477c04ab7711b976690a20b6fcf225f23d42c","tid":93991,"uid":38757,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-25T01:12:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>Lm薯片叔叔入唔到閳</blockquote><br />\n依家個牌面好清楚睇到, 上面係要邊個做特首"},{"pid":"82a35de20f531e96870afd089de94998e97c0184","tid":93991,"uid":6435,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-25T01:13:51.000Z","msg":"等睇過多排呢班人炒晒車"},{"pid":"cc447b2aa622a4cc6324172d378f2593f69a532a","tid":93991,"uid":24140,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-25T01:28:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>Lm薯片叔叔入唔到閳</blockquote><br />\n依家個牌面好清楚睇到, 上面係要邊個做特首</blockquote><br />\n你講既上面係支聯辨定北京先？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f52e63b85f4a2d135615b8cb9679bbabb00b357f","tid":93991,"uid":42820,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-25T01:36:01.000Z","msg":"咩新鮮蘿蔔皮代表黨?"},{"pid":"